WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.168 --> 01:43.536
=Episode 6=

02:00.714 --> 02:02.315
(I'm downstairs, waiting for you.)

02:02.835 --> 02:05.835
By the way,
there's something I want to tell you.

02:10.915 --> 02:11.755
I'm getting married.

02:15.074 --> 02:15.674
Marry whom?

02:16.755 --> 02:20.554
Is it someone you knew from London?

02:21.315 --> 02:21.995
No, it's not.

02:22.634 --> 02:24.234
I'll introduce you two later.

02:24.794 --> 02:25.715
Go back early.

02:53.715 --> 02:54.234
Sir.

02:54.394 --> 02:55.475
Sorry I'm late.

02:55.954 --> 02:57.595
- Hurry.
- Okay.

03:06.035 --> 03:07.035
Excuse me, may I ask

03:07.315 --> 03:08.435
what dishes to cook today?

03:08.954 --> 03:09.794
Garden salad.

03:13.195 --> 03:14.634
Haven't we met before?

03:16.995 --> 03:17.875
Jinda Group.

03:19.595 --> 03:20.554
Do we know each other?

03:22.354 --> 03:23.715
We met once at the company.

03:24.834 --> 03:26.195
Hi, I'm Xu Yan.

03:27.595 --> 03:28.995
Hello, I'm Fang Lei.

03:29.275 --> 03:30.674
I'm Shen Haoming's fiancﾃｩe.

03:37.875 --> 03:38.755
His junior schoolmate.

03:40.755 --> 03:42.114
We attended school together

03:42.554 --> 03:43.514
when we were in London.

03:44.195 --> 03:47.995
And our families have been
close friends for generations.

03:49.915 --> 03:50.755
In that case,

03:50.794 --> 03:52.155
you've known each other for years.

03:53.554 --> 03:54.394
Sixteen years old.

03:56.514 --> 03:57.634
Since sixteen years old.

04:00.595 --> 04:01.794
So like his little sister.

04:04.234 --> 04:05.275
Come visit us often.

04:05.595 --> 04:06.514
We can go shopping.

04:07.954 --> 04:08.475
Alright.

04:43.395 --> 04:46.674
Lei, you're so good at it.

04:46.715 --> 04:48.275
This looks so appetizing.

04:53.075 --> 04:54.035
Can I try some?

04:56.314 --> 04:58.395
- Of course.
- Thanks.

05:09.794 --> 05:10.635
Delicious.

05:11.234 --> 05:12.194
Are you busy later?

05:12.395 --> 05:13.194
Let's have a meal,

05:13.354 --> 05:14.354
so you can teach me.

05:16.794 --> 05:17.354
Okay.

05:23.754 --> 05:25.794
Xu Yan, thank you for treating me.

05:27.754 --> 05:28.595
Between you and me,

05:28.674 --> 05:29.635
no need to be so formal.

05:30.314 --> 05:31.434
Let's meet up more often.

05:36.915 --> 05:37.515
I'm glad

05:37.994 --> 05:38.915
you care for me.

05:39.595 --> 05:40.475
When I was abroad,

05:40.754 --> 05:41.515
I was so young.

05:42.075 --> 05:44.994
Haoming always worried I'd get homesick

05:45.234 --> 05:46.715
and feared foreigners might bully me,

05:47.035 --> 05:49.515
so he visited whenever he had time.

05:51.915 --> 05:52.915
You're like his sister,

05:52.955 --> 05:54.114
so it's natural.

05:54.754 --> 05:56.395
He should've done even better.

06:02.035 --> 06:03.674
I just started at Jinda Group,

06:04.275 --> 06:06.354
and Haoming put me on his project.

06:07.314 --> 06:09.114
Now I have to bother him again.

06:12.035 --> 06:13.234
Do your job well,

06:13.595 --> 06:15.194
then you won't trouble him, right?

06:19.794 --> 06:21.595
Lei, don't drink that much.

06:21.715 --> 06:23.395
Let's eat. They're delicious.

06:28.754 --> 06:30.434
Seeing Haoming marry someone

06:30.515 --> 06:32.835
so beautiful and accomplished,

06:33.754 --> 06:34.955
I'm really happy for him.

06:37.395 --> 06:38.635
This is my first time

06:38.674 --> 06:39.874
attending a wedding,

06:42.075 --> 06:43.475
can I be your bridesmaid?

06:55.155 --> 06:55.915
Okay.

07:26.896 --> 07:28.345
笙ｪYou once shone like the sun笙ｪ

07:28.345 --> 07:31.737
笙ｪThe flowers bloomed and withered笙ｪ

07:33.424 --> 07:35.449
笙ｪOur palms connected when we held hands笙ｪ

07:35.449 --> 07:38.041
笙ｪThen tangled into waiting笙ｪ

07:40.112 --> 07:42.000
笙ｪI've lost those beautiful moments too笙ｪ

07:42.000 --> 07:45.268
笙ｪPassing through my eyes
a thousand times笙ｪ

07:45.776 --> 07:47.760
笙ｪI couldn't embrace that feeling笙ｪ

07:47.760 --> 07:51.609
笙ｪMy love solidifies into amber笙ｪ

07:53.095 --> 07:55.120
笙ｪWhen you speak, the universe halts笙ｪ

07:55.261 --> 07:58.645
笙ｪEven fate grows still笙ｪ

07:58.862 --> 08:01.550
笙ｪHow do you笙ｪ

08:01.689 --> 08:05.650
笙ｪPortray me笙ｪ

08:06.256 --> 08:08.367
笙ｪTill sunset, with smiles笙ｪ

08:08.483 --> 08:11.502
笙ｪTears flow, no sorrow笙ｪ

08:11.617 --> 08:14.331
笙ｪWhen I look back笙ｪ

08:14.508 --> 08:18.384
笙ｪWill you wait for me笙ｪ

08:19.152 --> 08:20.908
笙ｪLike fireworks that loved笙ｪ

08:21.064 --> 08:22.841
笙ｪRushing toward the stars笙ｪ

08:22.841 --> 08:25.606
笙ｪUndaunted by pain笙ｪ

08:25.776 --> 08:27.632
笙ｪFearless of flames笙ｪ

08:27.632 --> 08:31.033
笙ｪEven if just a fleeting sparkle笙ｪ

08:32.481 --> 08:34.297
笙ｪWe shed tears笙ｪ

08:34.297 --> 08:37.968
笙ｪDeep blue seas turn to foam笙ｪ

08:37.968 --> 08:39.035
笙ｪWe regained freedom笙ｪ

08:39.035 --> 08:40.035
Now, the newlyweds,

08:40.554 --> 08:41.794
you may take the rings.

08:41.899 --> 08:44.483
笙ｪIf you remember me笙ｪ

08:44.915 --> 08:47.314
Haoming, as husband,

08:47.875 --> 08:50.155
put it on her ring finger.

08:56.115 --> 08:57.474
Bride, please take the ring.

08:58.074 --> 08:59.194
As wife,

08:59.755 --> 09:01.954
put it on Haoming's ring finger.

09:05.313 --> 09:07.289
笙ｪI love you, that's right笙ｪ

09:07.289 --> 09:10.745
笙ｪYou changed me笙ｪ

09:12.155 --> 09:13.155
Ladies and gentlemen.

09:13.594 --> 09:15.155
Let's give a warm round of applause.

09:15.515 --> 09:16.755
Now, the newlyweds,

09:17.275 --> 09:19.074
you may kiss each other.

09:21.296 --> 09:24.017
笙ｪIf you remember me笙ｪ

09:24.153 --> 09:27.671
笙ｪThen I'm pleased笙ｪ

09:37.434 --> 09:38.674
Keep the applause coming!

09:38.995 --> 09:40.235
Let us all witness this moment.

09:40.554 --> 09:42.395
Congratulations on their marriage!

09:42.674 --> 09:43.674
Grow old together!

09:45.115 --> 09:46.074
- Congratulations!
- Please come in.

09:46.074 --> 09:47.856
- Congratulations!
- Please, come right in.

09:47.995 --> 09:50.074
Yan, you look stunning!

09:50.074 --> 09:51.115
Yan, you're so pretty.

09:51.755 --> 09:52.915
Haoming looks so handsome.

09:52.995 --> 09:54.074
- Right?
- You look great.

09:54.074 --> 09:54.834
Thank you.

09:55.314 --> 09:56.074
Enjoy then!

09:56.194 --> 09:56.395
Okay.

09:56.395 --> 09:56.875
Talk later.

09:59.635 --> 10:00.554
Congratulations!

10:00.714 --> 10:01.515
Thank you.

10:01.635 --> 10:02.755
They're having a wedding.

10:14.194 --> 10:17.474
She looks like
Jiajia's classmate, Xu Yan?

10:18.474 --> 10:19.674
A bit indeed.

10:19.794 --> 10:20.434
It's her, right?

10:21.434 --> 10:22.035
Mr. Fu?

10:23.395 --> 10:23.995
Haoming.

10:24.515 --> 10:25.794
Finally, you are married.

10:26.875 --> 10:28.314
You married such a wonderful wife.

10:28.355 --> 10:29.074
Yes, she's great.

10:29.155 --> 10:29.794
Congratulations!

10:29.794 --> 10:30.635
Your seat over there.

10:30.755 --> 10:31.314
It's up front.

10:31.395 --> 10:31.834
Xu Yan.

10:41.314 --> 10:42.794
Thank you for the book, Mr. Xu.

10:43.115 --> 10:44.635
Could you please sign it for me?

10:45.714 --> 10:46.035
Alright.

10:52.995 --> 10:53.794
Mr. and Mrs. Xu.

10:54.115 --> 10:54.832
What a surprise.

10:55.714 --> 10:56.355
Where's Jiajia?

10:57.474 --> 10:58.515
She's too busy with work.

10:59.635 --> 11:00.794
We came to visit relatives.

11:01.194 --> 11:02.074
We're staying here,

11:02.954 --> 11:05.235
planning to stay in Jingzhou
before returning hometown.

11:05.275 --> 11:06.594
Never expected to meet you here.

11:07.074 --> 11:07.824
Congratulations!

11:08.875 --> 11:11.674
By the way, I have a gift for Jiajia.

11:11.794 --> 11:13.194
Maybe you come with me to get it.

11:13.355 --> 11:16.235
Yan, who are these two?

11:23.355 --> 11:24.314
Let me introduce.

11:25.235 --> 11:27.474
They are my college classmate's parents.

11:28.194 --> 11:29.275
This is my husband.

11:29.834 --> 11:30.194
Hello.

11:30.395 --> 11:31.275
My father-in-law.

11:31.635 --> 11:32.074
Hello.

11:32.155 --> 11:32.995
My father.

11:33.474 --> 11:33.915
Hello.

11:34.794 --> 11:36.074
Congratulations to you all!

11:37.235 --> 11:38.635
You're such a well-matched couple.

11:38.794 --> 11:39.995
- Congratulations!
- Thanks.

11:39.995 --> 11:40.755
Since we met here,

11:40.794 --> 11:41.794
if you don't mind,

11:42.115 --> 11:43.434
come join us.

11:44.755 --> 11:46.434
Would it bother you?

11:46.674 --> 11:47.035
No.

11:47.155 --> 11:47.915
Please, come in.

11:48.275 --> 11:48.954
This way, please.

11:49.355 --> 11:49.674
Please.

11:49.755 --> 11:51.035
- What's your surname?
- Xu.

11:51.794 --> 11:53.355
Same surname to Xu Yan.

11:53.474 --> 11:55.314
Exactly, I'm also a Xu.

11:56.194 --> 11:56.554
Surprise.

11:56.594 --> 11:56.915
Hello.

11:57.474 --> 11:58.474
Yan, I'll take him in.

11:58.954 --> 11:59.314
Alright.

12:00.035 --> 12:00.355
Come on.

12:02.355 --> 12:02.800
Come on.

12:08.235 --> 12:08.875
Thank you, Dad.

12:09.594 --> 12:10.275
Thank you, Mom.

12:11.314 --> 12:11.594
Thanks.

12:11.875 --> 12:12.594
Thank you, Ms. Ma.

12:13.235 --> 12:13.674
Thank you.

12:13.755 --> 12:14.395
Cheers.

12:14.515 --> 12:14.995
Thank you.

12:20.635 --> 12:21.554
Have a toast.

12:22.794 --> 12:23.115
Here.

12:23.834 --> 12:24.834
Come on.

12:25.515 --> 12:26.515
Haoming. Congratulations!

12:26.594 --> 12:27.434
- Cheers!
- Thanks!

12:27.794 --> 12:29.515
Haoming, what a wonderful wedding.

12:29.794 --> 12:31.594
You're a workaholic.

12:32.115 --> 12:34.074
Was all this prepared by Yan?

12:35.035 --> 12:36.875
So this toast shouldn't go to you.

12:37.275 --> 12:39.275
To our beautiful and capable Yan!

12:39.314 --> 12:40.434
To Yan!

12:40.594 --> 12:42.235
Xu Yan has already had enough drink.

12:42.275 --> 12:43.275
No more drink.

12:43.515 --> 12:45.074
I'll take this drink for her.

12:45.954 --> 12:46.554
Liquor?

12:47.074 --> 12:47.995
Drink three glasses.

12:48.794 --> 12:49.834
Yes, three glasses!

12:50.235 --> 12:50.594
Come on.

12:50.794 --> 12:51.635
Three glasses it is!

12:51.875 --> 12:52.194
Good.

12:52.235 --> 12:53.035
First!

12:54.954 --> 12:55.875
Impressive!

12:56.194 --> 12:56.794
Another one!

12:58.594 --> 12:59.235
Second!

13:00.434 --> 13:01.474
- Amazing!
- Good!

13:01.594 --> 13:02.355
One more to go!

13:05.035 --> 13:05.474
Alright.

13:05.594 --> 13:06.395
Last one!

13:06.395 --> 13:06.995
Third one!

13:07.115 --> 13:08.314
- Another!
- The final one!

13:09.074 --> 13:09.515
Mr. Shen.

13:09.714 --> 13:10.275
Mr. Xu.

13:10.275 --> 13:10.674
Mr. Xu.

13:10.714 --> 13:11.915
Honored to attend

13:11.915 --> 13:12.656
Xu Yan's wedding.

13:12.995 --> 13:13.554
We two...

13:13.594 --> 13:14.474
Enjoy your drinks.

13:15.474 --> 13:16.434
Thank you.

13:17.035 --> 13:17.875
Thank you, everyone.

13:17.995 --> 13:18.515
Alright.

13:18.875 --> 13:19.594
Next table.

13:20.035 --> 13:20.474
Come on.

13:21.074 --> 13:22.635
Mr. Xu, you came to Jingzhou for...

13:22.794 --> 13:23.355
For vacation.

13:23.995 --> 13:24.875
Stay for a few days,

13:25.194 --> 13:26.115
then go to hometown.

13:26.515 --> 13:27.635
Why the rush?

13:27.834 --> 13:28.995
Stay in Jingzhou longer.

13:30.474 --> 13:32.074
I'm reaching retirement age,

13:32.155 --> 13:33.314
planning to return and settle

13:33.995 --> 13:36.515
back in my hometown.

13:37.035 --> 13:37.755
Great.

13:38.074 --> 13:39.954
The medical facilities, shopping,

13:40.035 --> 13:41.355
and everything is much better.

13:42.355 --> 13:45.456
Mr. Xu, what do you do overseas?

13:45.456 --> 13:46.314
Architecture studies.

13:46.635 --> 13:47.594
Construction?

13:47.995 --> 13:49.755
Then you're in the same field
as my in-law.

13:50.434 --> 13:50.995
Really?

13:52.834 --> 13:55.115
What a double fate!

13:55.434 --> 13:56.554
Cheers!

13:59.696 --> 14:00.877
You look gorgeous.

14:00.995 --> 14:01.834
One more.

14:01.875 --> 14:02.714
Cheers!

14:03.755 --> 14:04.194
Thank you.

14:04.275 --> 14:05.395
Come on.

14:05.434 --> 14:05.875
Yan.

14:06.794 --> 14:07.794
Your classmate's parents

14:07.995 --> 14:09.074
came here first time.

14:09.794 --> 14:10.714
Go greet them.

14:12.314 --> 14:13.794
Okay, I'll be right back.

14:16.194 --> 14:17.434
Your dress looks lovely.

14:18.635 --> 14:19.115
Come on.

14:19.915 --> 14:20.674
How many more?

14:21.434 --> 14:22.115
One last glass.

14:22.155 --> 14:22.594
One glass.

14:22.834 --> 14:23.275
I'll drink.

14:23.594 --> 14:24.275
He has

14:24.594 --> 14:27.275
deep expertise in architecture,

14:27.355 --> 14:28.635
even wrote a book,

14:28.674 --> 14:29.714
called... something...

14:29.954 --> 14:31.594
Sustainable Building Design.

14:34.035 --> 14:35.155
My father specializes in

14:35.194 --> 14:36.714
sustainable building research.

14:39.074 --> 14:41.594
My research focuses
on architectural mechanics.

14:42.035 --> 14:44.194
Though in the same field,
our focuses differ.

14:44.794 --> 14:46.714
Let's chat if you have time.

14:47.314 --> 14:48.115
Absolutely.

14:48.395 --> 14:49.115
Mr. Xu.

14:49.554 --> 14:51.074
We've finally gathered today.

14:51.115 --> 14:52.275
Why don't we take a photo?

14:52.355 --> 14:53.954
You can show it to Jiajia. How's it?

14:54.115 --> 14:54.755
Great idea.

14:54.794 --> 14:55.235
Come on.

14:55.275 --> 14:55.554
Okay.

14:55.554 --> 14:56.115
Take a photo.

14:56.235 --> 14:56.755
Alright.

14:56.794 --> 14:57.714
Take a photo.

14:57.755 --> 14:58.834
I'll get Haoming.

14:59.434 --> 14:59.794
Alright.

14:59.834 --> 15:00.474
Let's be here.

15:00.474 --> 15:00.834
Alright?

15:00.915 --> 15:01.474
This way.

15:01.594 --> 15:02.194
This way.

15:02.275 --> 15:02.915
This spot, okay?

15:04.275 --> 15:04.915
You silly!

15:04.915 --> 15:06.155
- I'm sorry.
- I'm sorry.

15:06.155 --> 15:06.915
Sorry, sorry.

15:06.915 --> 15:07.434
Let me.

15:08.035 --> 15:08.915
Look at this mess.

15:08.915 --> 15:09.674
Here.

15:09.995 --> 15:10.954
So sorry.

15:11.115 --> 15:12.515
I'm sorry.

15:12.755 --> 15:13.554
It's fine.

15:14.035 --> 15:14.635
I'm so sorry.

15:14.674 --> 15:15.434
I live upstairs.

15:16.074 --> 15:16.915
I'll go change.

15:17.235 --> 15:18.194
- Sorry.
- It's fine.

15:18.194 --> 15:19.355
We'll cover the dry cleaning.

15:19.474 --> 15:20.915
We're so sorry.

15:20.954 --> 15:21.834
Don't mind it.

15:21.915 --> 15:22.794
The wedding matters.

15:22.794 --> 15:23.235
See you.

15:23.474 --> 15:23.954
Alright.

15:24.074 --> 15:25.275
I'm sorry.

15:26.194 --> 15:26.714
This way.

15:35.554 --> 15:36.554
I'm really sorry.

15:36.755 --> 15:37.635
I'll have them get you

15:37.674 --> 15:38.314
a new suit.

15:38.314 --> 15:38.875
No need.

15:38.995 --> 15:40.035
I have one upstairs.

15:41.035 --> 15:41.395
Okay.

15:41.995 --> 15:42.794
Your turn.

15:43.515 --> 15:43.995
Haoming.

15:44.355 --> 15:44.954
Happy wedding!

15:45.355 --> 15:45.714
Thanks.

15:45.755 --> 15:47.035
- Congratulations!
- Thank you.

15:47.674 --> 15:48.594
Let me introduce you.

15:48.954 --> 15:51.474
She's my sister,
just graduated from law school.

15:52.954 --> 15:53.834
- Impressive!
- Great.

15:53.834 --> 15:54.714
You know what?

15:55.194 --> 15:56.035
She's still single.

15:56.714 --> 15:57.474
Be proactive.

15:58.434 --> 15:59.395
What a coincidence!

15:59.834 --> 16:01.194
Haoming and I go way back.

16:01.515 --> 16:02.074
I'm single.

16:03.155 --> 16:03.755
Add my WeChat.

16:04.155 --> 16:06.115
Haoming, what's her name?

16:06.915 --> 16:07.474
Fang Lei.

16:08.635 --> 16:09.155
Miss Fang.

16:09.515 --> 16:10.035
Add me.

16:10.074 --> 16:10.515
Come on.

16:11.115 --> 16:11.714
Add my WeChat.

16:11.755 --> 16:12.794
Add my WeChat too.

16:16.635 --> 16:20.395
Miss Fang, hello.

16:20.794 --> 16:23.035
I'm Han Weiping, from legal department
of Jinda Group.

16:24.155 --> 16:25.155
Can I add your WeChat?

16:26.635 --> 16:27.155
It'd better

16:27.515 --> 16:28.194
to keep in touch.

16:28.755 --> 16:29.275
I'll add you.

16:29.554 --> 16:30.074
Okay, okay.

16:31.474 --> 16:31.834
Here.

16:34.115 --> 16:34.434
Done.

16:35.155 --> 16:36.755
Miss Fang, add me too.

16:36.954 --> 16:37.755
- Here.
- Add me.

16:37.755 --> 16:38.074
Add me.

16:38.074 --> 16:38.594
Come on.

16:38.594 --> 16:39.434
Let me scan too.

16:39.554 --> 16:40.515
Miss Fang, add me.

16:40.554 --> 16:41.008
Okay.

17:09.155 --> 17:10.115
(At the infinity pool.)

17:28.034 --> 17:29.274
(Think drunk people)

17:29.315 --> 17:30.795
(drown easily?)

18:15.555 --> 18:16.954
Being drunk in a pool isn't safe.

18:17.474 --> 18:18.032
Come up!

18:20.595 --> 18:21.555
I don't want to go back.

18:22.155 --> 18:23.754
I need to sober up here.

18:25.555 --> 18:26.194
Suit yourself.

18:26.795 --> 18:28.835
Aren't you afraid
I'll drown like my sister did?

18:38.034 --> 18:39.595
Don't ever say that.

18:41.234 --> 18:41.994
It brings bad luck.

18:43.274 --> 18:44.274
This is my wedding day.

18:44.555 --> 18:46.034
Is this drama necessary?

19:04.635 --> 19:05.355
Haoming.

19:07.315 --> 19:08.875
Remember our first meeting?

19:13.714 --> 19:14.674
I remember very clearly

19:15.954 --> 19:18.835
what color you're wearing that day.

19:19.954 --> 19:21.434
Even the sunlight that day

19:22.674 --> 19:24.315
and the scent in the air,

19:25.915 --> 19:29.795
I remember every single detail.

19:36.795 --> 19:38.915
I thought I could let you go,

19:43.034 --> 19:44.555
but seeing you get married today,

19:45.754 --> 19:47.395
watching you walk down the aisle,

19:48.754 --> 19:49.474
I realize

19:50.994 --> 19:52.555
I can never let you go.

19:57.474 --> 19:58.315
Shen Haoming,

20:00.635 --> 20:01.315
I love you.

20:05.635 --> 20:06.434
I'm married now.

20:07.434 --> 20:08.075
Back off.

20:10.034 --> 20:11.155
You mean that woman?

20:11.795 --> 20:13.835
Don't think she's that naive.

20:15.155 --> 20:16.795
She pretended to be close with me

20:16.835 --> 20:17.514
once we met,

20:17.954 --> 20:19.434
just to figure out our relationship.

20:20.674 --> 20:22.355
That Xu Yan is calculating.

20:23.714 --> 20:25.034
Why marry her?

20:26.355 --> 20:28.034
Your performance at the wedding today

20:29.355 --> 20:30.315
was quite dramatic.

20:31.274 --> 20:32.155
No need

20:32.514 --> 20:34.514
to overthink anything.

20:34.875 --> 20:35.514
Just drop it.

20:36.315 --> 20:37.075
Once sobered up,

20:38.194 --> 20:38.954
go home.

21:00.754 --> 21:01.795
Won't we miss our flight?

21:02.155 --> 21:02.595
Relax.

21:03.315 --> 21:03.835
Haoming.

21:04.315 --> 21:04.915
Yan.

21:07.514 --> 21:08.954
Leaving for your honeymoon now?

21:09.875 --> 21:10.355
Yes.

21:12.274 --> 21:14.034
You drank so much for me yesterday.

21:14.915 --> 21:15.754
Feeling okay?

21:16.875 --> 21:18.395
I was completely drunk.

21:18.514 --> 21:19.434
Don't even remember

21:19.474 --> 21:20.555
how I got home.

21:21.835 --> 21:22.315
Right.

21:22.754 --> 21:23.915
Last night,

21:24.075 --> 21:25.674
did I cause any trouble?

21:26.274 --> 21:26.635
No.

21:28.555 --> 21:29.635
Glad to hear that.

21:33.395 --> 21:33.915
Yan.

21:34.635 --> 21:35.315
You two talk.

21:35.795 --> 21:36.635
I'll wait in the car.

21:41.315 --> 21:42.155
Haoming said

21:42.194 --> 21:43.395
you're honeymooning in London.

21:44.194 --> 21:46.194
There's a great steakhouse over there.

21:46.795 --> 21:49.034
Haoming used to take me there often.

21:55.315 --> 21:56.395
What places did Haoming

21:56.434 --> 21:57.194
take you before?

21:58.915 --> 22:00.395
Please sort it out and send it to me.

22:03.075 --> 22:04.514
Don't go in the pool after drinking.

22:06.234 --> 22:07.155
You could be drowned.

22:46.434 --> 22:46.994
Mr. Shen.

22:47.395 --> 22:47.875
Yan.

22:48.674 --> 22:49.474
You're finally back.

22:49.954 --> 22:50.835
We've missed you!

22:52.115 --> 22:53.714
We brought souvenirs for everyone.

22:54.034 --> 22:55.115
The driver'll bring them up

22:55.355 --> 22:55.875
to you.

22:57.234 --> 22:57.635
Got it.

22:58.075 --> 22:58.635
Thank you.

23:06.075 --> 23:06.835
Han Weiping,

23:07.954 --> 23:09.915
Jinda Group's
newly hired legal consultant,

23:10.674 --> 23:11.555
young and capable.

23:12.595 --> 23:14.234
They met at our wedding.

23:15.754 --> 23:16.875
Lei has good taste.

23:18.595 --> 23:19.155
Let's go.

23:22.155 --> 23:24.714
By the way,
let's go visit Grandma in a few days.

23:26.395 --> 23:27.474
But we just got back.

23:27.714 --> 23:29.514
It's fine. It won't affect work.

23:30.155 --> 23:31.234
I've asked for leave.

23:35.674 --> 23:36.075
Okay.

23:37.355 --> 23:39.434
We can bring Grandma her gifts.

23:39.795 --> 23:40.115
Alright.

23:40.115 --> 23:41.113
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

23:41.113 --> 23:43.408
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

23:43.408 --> 23:45.584
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

23:46.064 --> 23:47.963
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

23:47.963 --> 23:53.680
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

23:54.128 --> 23:57.194
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

23:57.194 --> 23:57.875
Grandma.

24:00.674 --> 24:01.474
Yan.

24:01.835 --> 24:02.915
You fell asleep?

24:02.994 --> 24:04.994
I really miss you!

24:05.075 --> 24:06.075
Let me see.

24:06.555 --> 24:07.595
You've lost weight!

24:07.674 --> 24:08.395
Again?

24:08.434 --> 24:09.595
Haven't you been eating well?

24:09.714 --> 24:11.034
You're the one who's lost weight.

24:11.754 --> 24:13.315
No way. You...

24:14.595 --> 24:15.194
Hello, Grandma.

24:15.355 --> 24:17.315
I'm your grandson-in-law, Shen Haoming.

24:17.595 --> 24:18.674
I brought you some gifts.

24:20.875 --> 24:22.595
What a handsome man!

24:23.835 --> 24:24.875
Welcome home.

24:24.915 --> 24:25.395
Come in.

24:25.395 --> 24:26.194
Come in.

24:26.595 --> 24:28.595
You didn't need to bring

24:28.674 --> 24:30.355
so many gifts to me.

24:30.434 --> 24:32.355
I can't possibly eat all this by myself.

24:32.395 --> 24:35.355
I brought glucosamine for you.

24:35.434 --> 24:37.434
It helps prevent osteoporosis.

24:37.635 --> 24:38.234
Too much!

24:38.315 --> 24:39.234
Haoming said

24:39.355 --> 24:41.514
you need to keep taking this fish oil.

24:41.595 --> 24:44.075
It helps lower your cholesterol.

24:44.075 --> 24:45.264
Do you know?

24:51.555 --> 24:52.034
Grandma.

24:52.434 --> 24:53.355
It smells wonderful.

24:54.115 --> 24:54.754
What's this?

24:55.234 --> 24:56.075
This...

24:56.395 --> 24:57.395
Fresh greens.

24:57.434 --> 24:59.234
You city folks can't get this.

24:59.635 --> 25:00.555
I picked them fresh

25:00.595 --> 25:02.434
at the vegetable patch this afternoon.

25:02.795 --> 25:04.555
You city people always talk about

25:04.835 --> 25:06.274
green and eco-friendly,

25:06.754 --> 25:07.754
and pollution-free.

25:09.555 --> 25:10.875
What's that dish then?

25:10.915 --> 25:13.075
Oxtail and taro stew.

25:14.115 --> 25:15.155
Nourishing.

25:17.234 --> 25:19.514
Grandma, you live here alone.

25:20.034 --> 25:22.034
So Yan's parents...

25:22.155 --> 25:22.754
Grandma.

25:24.155 --> 25:24.635
This one.

25:25.115 --> 25:26.835
I brought your favorite photo.

25:27.434 --> 25:28.875
I'll hang it...

25:29.355 --> 25:30.234
In the bedroom

25:30.514 --> 25:31.754
where I can easily see.

25:32.714 --> 25:33.635
Go on!

25:33.754 --> 25:34.795
It's all greasy smoke.

25:34.875 --> 25:35.994
- Don't stay here.
- Come.

25:36.915 --> 25:37.456
Right.

25:38.234 --> 25:39.115
Serve it up!

25:44.234 --> 25:44.795
Look.

25:45.994 --> 25:46.595
Is this okay?

25:47.754 --> 25:49.434
It seems slightly tilted to the left.

25:59.714 --> 26:00.274
Yan.

26:00.915 --> 26:01.555
Is this okay?

26:03.994 --> 26:04.555
Good.

26:09.514 --> 26:10.194
Perfect.

26:30.915 --> 26:31.674
Yan,

26:32.315 --> 26:34.194
I prepared a room for you

26:34.315 --> 26:36.234
with a double bed.

26:36.474 --> 26:37.674
Why don't you sleep there

26:37.954 --> 26:40.355
but squeeze into my bed instead?

26:40.674 --> 26:42.115
I rarely come back.

26:42.155 --> 26:43.635
I want to sleep with you.

26:44.555 --> 26:46.395
You insist on sleeping with me.

26:46.674 --> 26:48.075
You don't come back often.

26:48.075 --> 26:50.994
Just sleep with him, will you?

26:51.555 --> 26:53.155
Why sleep with me?

26:53.555 --> 26:54.514
- Let me.
- It seems...

26:55.075 --> 26:56.075
Hand over your hand.

26:57.555 --> 26:58.274
It's that simple?

27:00.635 --> 27:02.835
I can't make it right.

27:03.954 --> 27:04.635
Let me help you.

27:15.395 --> 27:16.194
Yan,

27:18.674 --> 27:21.075
there's something

27:21.115 --> 27:22.714
I need to tell you.

27:25.595 --> 27:29.555
Your father hasn't been well recently,

27:29.595 --> 27:30.635
and he did a body checkup.

27:31.514 --> 27:32.635
The test results

27:32.674 --> 27:35.474
said there's a tumor in his lung.

27:46.115 --> 27:47.994
Is it benign?

27:48.595 --> 27:50.434
It appears benign for now.

27:50.474 --> 27:51.714
But the doctor said

27:51.754 --> 27:52.915
he mustn't overexert himself

27:52.954 --> 27:54.315
from now on.

27:55.155 --> 27:56.474
As for whether this benign state

27:57.315 --> 27:58.274
might turn malignant,

27:58.835 --> 28:00.234
the doctor can't guarantee.

28:05.115 --> 28:08.434
I know how you think of him.

28:09.474 --> 28:10.875
But you didn't invite him

28:11.595 --> 28:13.395
to your wedding.

28:15.434 --> 28:16.674
Now that he's ill,

28:17.395 --> 28:18.474
I think

28:19.194 --> 28:20.835
you should

28:20.875 --> 28:22.194
go visit him.

28:26.434 --> 28:27.674
Is this length okay?

28:28.115 --> 28:28.514
Perfect.

28:28.754 --> 28:29.875
Okay, switch hands.

28:34.274 --> 28:36.274
If you don't want to go alone,

28:36.915 --> 28:38.434
I can go with you.

28:48.474 --> 28:49.315
I understand.

28:51.674 --> 28:52.514
Listen.

28:52.915 --> 28:53.355
See?

28:53.954 --> 28:55.115
When trimming nails,

28:55.555 --> 28:57.474
you must cut the edges

28:57.635 --> 28:58.355
like this.

28:59.194 --> 28:59.875
Like this.

29:00.754 --> 29:02.075
Otherwise, you'll get paronychia.

29:02.194 --> 29:03.514
T-This is so difficult.

29:03.674 --> 29:04.754
I always use

29:04.795 --> 29:05.994
small scissors

29:06.034 --> 29:06.954
to trim them.

29:25.194 --> 29:26.034
Shen,

29:26.795 --> 29:28.194
got up so early?

29:30.115 --> 29:31.795
Work habits keep me rising early.

29:32.714 --> 29:34.795
Come grocery shopping with me?

29:35.034 --> 29:36.155
Okay, let's go.

29:38.274 --> 29:39.915
You young people

29:40.274 --> 29:41.555
run big companies

29:41.674 --> 29:43.075
and chase grand career.

29:43.954 --> 29:45.795
You need to balance work and rest.

29:46.915 --> 29:49.875
Health should be your top priority.

29:49.994 --> 29:51.234
Only when you're well-rested,

29:51.234 --> 29:52.754
and well-fed

29:53.115 --> 29:56.474
can you achieve great things.

29:57.234 --> 29:59.234
Come visit more often.

29:59.315 --> 30:01.474
The fresh air here does wonders.

30:02.555 --> 30:04.075
Okay, I'll do it.

30:05.234 --> 30:07.434
You know, Yan cares about you

30:07.795 --> 30:09.115
most, Grandma.

30:10.474 --> 30:11.635
You're getting old,

30:12.234 --> 30:13.674
and it's hard to live alone.

30:13.954 --> 30:15.915
Move to Jingzhou with us, okay?

30:16.194 --> 30:17.075
No, no.

30:17.555 --> 30:19.434
My legs still work fine.

30:19.875 --> 30:21.355
I've lived here for my life.

30:21.434 --> 30:23.674
I can't get used to the city life.

30:24.635 --> 30:27.155
Don't worry about me.

30:27.875 --> 30:28.674
Rest assured.

30:29.274 --> 30:30.514
If you need anything,

30:30.915 --> 30:32.075
tell us anytime.

30:34.234 --> 30:36.555
Before you leave,

30:37.714 --> 30:40.474
I want to say something to you.

30:41.355 --> 30:41.915
Go ahead.

30:43.234 --> 30:45.514
Every time Yan called,

30:46.115 --> 30:47.514
she praised you,

30:47.595 --> 30:48.994
saying you're great

30:49.234 --> 30:50.915
and treating her well.

30:52.595 --> 30:54.194
After I've met you,

30:55.474 --> 30:57.954
you're exactly as she said.

30:59.954 --> 31:00.714
I really like you.

31:02.434 --> 31:03.514
We're a married couple.

31:04.075 --> 31:05.474
I should treat her well.

31:09.635 --> 31:10.595
Shen,

31:12.234 --> 31:15.474
I've raised Yan since she was a kid.

31:16.714 --> 31:18.674
I'm just an old country woman,

31:18.714 --> 31:20.835
couldn't teach her much.

31:21.514 --> 31:22.555
She might have

31:23.115 --> 31:26.835
some bad habits or whatnot.

31:29.075 --> 31:32.315
If she makes mistakes,

31:33.434 --> 31:35.994
can you be more forgiving?

31:37.234 --> 31:38.000
Okay.

31:38.474 --> 31:41.155
Give her a chance to improve.

31:41.954 --> 31:42.795
Okay?

31:43.875 --> 31:45.315
Absolutely, Grandma.

31:46.315 --> 31:47.274
I remember every word

31:48.034 --> 31:48.954
you said.

31:49.915 --> 31:50.896
Rest assured.

31:52.875 --> 31:53.835
What do we buy later?

31:54.795 --> 31:55.875
What would you like to eat?

31:56.075 --> 31:57.555
I want oysters.

31:59.555 --> 32:01.274
There aren't oysters here.

32:01.395 --> 32:02.954
But we have fresh fish here.

32:03.514 --> 32:04.034
Fish?

32:23.274 --> 32:24.274
(For your treatment.)

32:24.994 --> 32:26.448
(Password is Qiao Lin's birthday.)

33:12.754 --> 33:13.194
We're here.

33:38.714 --> 33:39.754
What do you think?

33:46.835 --> 33:47.835
Blue bricks, gray tiles,

33:48.635 --> 33:49.595
and bamboo groves.

33:50.395 --> 33:52.075
Every inch of this space
seems to whisper

33:52.474 --> 33:54.315
tales of tranquility and peace.

33:56.434 --> 33:58.555
That's why
it's called Jingzhou's retreat.

34:00.194 --> 34:01.994
As expected from
a top journalism student,

34:02.395 --> 34:03.034
so eloquent.

34:04.234 --> 34:05.274
Stop teasing me.

34:05.915 --> 34:07.915
I just feel that in such spaces

34:08.315 --> 34:10.034
we should speak poetically

34:10.514 --> 34:11.994
to suit the vibe here.

34:16.154 --> 34:17.634
In this vast city,

34:17.954 --> 34:19.355
having such a serene corner

34:20.275 --> 34:22.434
instantly soothes all anxieties.

34:23.675 --> 34:24.514
It's truly wonderful.

34:25.795 --> 34:27.795
I think in a completely different way.

34:28.355 --> 34:29.634
Alright, tell me,

34:29.875 --> 34:30.634
what do you think?

34:31.395 --> 34:32.195
Here, look.

34:32.994 --> 34:34.074
All the plumbing and wiring

34:34.675 --> 34:35.675
needs renovation.

34:36.875 --> 34:37.994
Behind you is the kitchen.

34:38.835 --> 34:39.715
The bathroom

34:40.434 --> 34:40.915
needs to get

34:41.315 --> 34:42.355
the waterproofing repairs.

34:42.434 --> 34:43.875
Why do you know this place so well?

34:44.114 --> 34:44.634
You.

34:46.875 --> 34:49.875
You'll be the lady of this retreat.

34:50.634 --> 34:53.074
Work connections help you meet guests

34:53.554 --> 34:54.514
and expand your network.

34:55.074 --> 34:55.675
That's good.

34:56.434 --> 34:58.875
But mere show interactions

34:58.915 --> 35:00.355
aren't enough for real connections.

35:00.835 --> 35:02.195
Off-camera relationships

35:02.275 --> 35:03.074
require

35:03.514 --> 35:04.434
maintenance too.

35:09.875 --> 35:12.034
The location is excellent,

35:12.634 --> 35:14.994
private and secure.

35:16.235 --> 35:17.154
Perfect for hosting

35:17.474 --> 35:19.235
gatherings with friends.

35:20.034 --> 35:22.715
This will benefit your career.

35:27.474 --> 35:29.554
Yan, listen.

35:30.114 --> 35:30.954
The better you work,

35:31.514 --> 35:32.915
the more influence

35:32.994 --> 35:34.315
you'll gain at the network.

35:34.675 --> 35:37.715
It'll benefit your anchor application.

35:43.034 --> 35:44.154
You think I don't know

35:44.755 --> 35:48.395
you practice broadcasting at 5 AM?

35:52.034 --> 35:56.154
You're my wife now.

35:57.594 --> 35:59.195
Whatever dreams you have,

35:59.994 --> 36:02.154
I'll help you make them real.

36:08.994 --> 36:09.634
Go check inside.

36:11.235 --> 36:11.715
Come on.

36:19.795 --> 36:21.074
Is it enough for a dining area?

36:21.395 --> 36:22.235
More than sufficient.

36:22.915 --> 36:24.675
In such prime location,

36:25.355 --> 36:27.355
this space is sufficient.

36:28.554 --> 36:30.034
I think we should

36:30.634 --> 36:32.395
put cabinets here.

36:32.634 --> 36:33.994
And dining area's here.

36:34.034 --> 36:36.395
But these white walls seem too plain.

36:36.434 --> 36:36.795
So...

36:42.544 --> 36:45.840
(Soon, I'll be as tall as Dad)

36:48.954 --> 36:51.114
The previous owners left

36:51.355 --> 36:53.315
their child's height markings

36:53.514 --> 36:54.195
on the frame.

36:54.395 --> 36:55.074
How adorable.

36:57.634 --> 36:59.034
When I was little,

37:00.594 --> 37:02.355
Dad measured my height like this too.

37:03.034 --> 37:04.074
These are precious,

37:04.755 --> 37:06.074
so I kept them intact.

37:10.034 --> 37:11.034
(You kid!)

37:11.154 --> 37:12.994
(Stand still. Dad's measuring.)

37:12.994 --> 37:13.594
Come here.

37:13.875 --> 37:14.755
Do it again.

37:17.474 --> 37:18.315
- No cheating.
- Hey!

37:18.355 --> 37:18.994
Do it again.

37:19.074 --> 37:19.755
Ready? Okay.

37:19.795 --> 37:20.594
Stand straight.

37:21.154 --> 37:21.634
There.

37:21.755 --> 37:22.355
Move.

37:23.235 --> 37:23.554
Come.

37:23.634 --> 37:24.275
Come to me.

37:27.434 --> 37:28.434
Last time was 133cm.

37:28.474 --> 37:29.395
Now it's 134cm.

37:29.434 --> 37:31.074
How much did you grow?

37:32.395 --> 37:33.074
One centimeter.

37:33.514 --> 37:36.235
Let's celebrate Lin's growth!

37:36.434 --> 37:38.235
I'll cook you delicious dishes, okay?

37:45.915 --> 37:46.554
I remember too.

37:53.795 --> 37:54.474
Have a lipstick?

38:06.275 --> 38:06.835
Stand still.

38:07.088 --> 38:09.664
笙ｪI like it when it's just me and you笙ｪ

38:13.936 --> 38:16.507
笙ｪI think by now you know it笙ｪ

38:18.192 --> 38:19.845
笙ｪAbout me and you笙ｪ

38:20.880 --> 38:23.376
笙ｪThere's not a thing that I wouldn't do笙ｪ

38:27.440 --> 38:30.686
笙ｪRight now just to be here with you笙ｪ

38:34.736 --> 38:35.792
笙ｪI like you笙ｪ

38:35.792 --> 38:38.361
笙ｪHere in my arms笙ｪ

38:41.840 --> 38:42.672
笙ｪI like you笙ｪ

38:42.672 --> 38:44.980
笙ｪHere in my arms笙ｪ

38:49.168 --> 38:50.796
笙ｪWhat already happened笙ｪ

